title: Handshake No Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents agreement, greeting, or a deal being made between two people, specifically with a medium-dark skin tone. It conveys a sense of collaboration and positive connection.
apple_vendor_description: Apple's handshake emoji, specifically showcasing a medium-dark skin tone, presents two hands clasped in a gesture of agreement and partnership with a distinct 3D depth. The smooth gradients and realistic lighting on Apple devices highlight the texture and form of the hands, creating a palpable sense of connection. This emoji is widely used on Apple devices to signify trust, collaboration, and a successful deal or reconciliation.
